summary.value:
This is the first preregistration for this project.

The preregistration consists of the questionnaire (file: "GEEL - Questionnaire.pdf") and the analysis script (files: "GEEL - Preregistration.R" and "GEEL - Preregistration.pdf"). To enable testing of the script, we also upload the file "GEEL - Test Data.sav", which includes fake test responses generated via Qualtrics. The two analysis script files are identical except for the format so that participants who do not use R can still access the preregistration in pdf format.

The analysis script contains descriptions of the design, the hypothesis, the sample, the variables, the inference criteria, the exclusion criteria, and the detailed analysis plan.
